msgid "Configuration Items"
msgstr "구성 항목 (Configuration Items)"

#: ../../source/project-config.rst:179
msgid ""
"The ``zuul.yaml`` and ``.zuul.yaml`` configuration files are YAML-formatted "
"and are structured as a series of items, each of which is referenced below."
msgstr ""
"``zuul.yaml`` 및 ``.zuul.yaml`` 구성 파일은 YAML 형식이며 일련의 항목들로 구"
"성되어 있고, 각각은 아래에서 참조됩니다."

#: ../../source/project-config.rst:183
msgid ""
"In the case of a ``zuul.d`` (or ``.zuul.d``) directory, Zuul recurses the "
"directory and extends the configuration using all the .yaml files in the "
"sorted path order.  For example, to keep job's variants in a separate file, "
"it needs to be loaded after the main entries, for example using number "
"prefixes in file's names::"
